        .hex #eed000

  .guide
    .content
      h2 Production
      p The flag should have a proportion of 2:3. So if the flag has a hoist of 4 feet, its fly should be 6 feet.
      p If resized, it must maintain these proportions.
    .visual
      img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia-dimensions.svg')

  .guide.wide.timeline
    .content
      h2 Previous iterations
      ul.visual.flag-list
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia-unofficial.jpg')
          h4 Pre-1879
          p The flag supplied to militia units bearing the coat of arms.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia-1879-1902.jpg')
          h4 1879–1902
          p Introduced by Herman H. Perry, Georgia state senator. Based on the first Confederate national flag.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia-1902-1906.jpg')
          h4 1902–1906
          p Upon the blue field, the coat of arms must be “stamped, painted or embroidered.”
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia-1906-1920.jpg')
          h4 1906–1920
          p A white shield is added along with a red banner with the word “Georgia.”
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia-1920-1956.jpg')
          h4 1920–1956
          p The coat of arms is replaced with the state seal in white and blue.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia-1956-2001.jpg')
          h4 1956–2001
          p Designed by John Sammons Bell, the red and white bars are replaced with the Confederate battle flag.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia-2001-2003.jpg')
          h4 2001–2003
          p Designed by architect Cecil Alexander and championed by Governor Roy Barnes, a very unpopular “compromise” version.
        li.flag-item
          span.flag: img(src='/assets/images/flag-georgia.svg')
          h4 2003–Present
          p The current Georgia state flag.

